Title: An Act Changing the Name of Urdaneta General Hospital in the Municipality of Urdaneta, Province of Pangasinan, to Amadeo J. Perez, Sr. Memorial General Hospital
Data:
BATAS PAMBANSA Blg. 737
An Act Changing the Name of Urdaneta General Hospital in the Municipality of Urdaneta, Province of Pangasinan, to Amadeo J. Perez, Sr. Memorial General Hospital
Section 1. The name of Urdaneta General Hospital in the Municipality of Urdaneta, Province of Pangasinan, is hereby changed to Amadeo J. Perez, Sr. Memorial General Hospital.1awphi1
Section 2. This Act shall take effect upon its approval.
Approved: April 13, 1984
